# Student Portal Demo

This is a basic idea for a **Student Portal Application**. The portal will provide students with access to:

## 🔑 Features

- 📚 View and manage enrolled courses
- 📝 Submit assignments
- 📅 Track academic calendar and events
- 💬 Message instructors and classmates
- 📊 View grades and academic progress
- 🔔 Receive important announcements

## 💡 Purpose

This application aims to provide a centralized platform for students to manage their academic life effectively and stay connected with their institution.

---

This repository serves as a starting point for the student portal demo project.
